\chessboard[light=green, dark=blue, fen="rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1"]
\end{document}
```
This will produce a green and blue chessboard with the initial position of the game.

